data.description: UPDATE:  New Carpet was installed in all bedrooms, stairway and loft area.  Come take a look.  Great location between Schertz and New Braunfels.  This beautiful home features 4 bedrooms and 3 1/2 baths.  Master bedroom and bath are downstairs.  Bathroom has a seperate garden tub and shower and walk in closet.   Large open kitchen with Island and eat in area.  Lots of living room and formal dining room space.   Upstairs there are 3 large bedrooms with lots of closet space, 2 full bathrooms and a loft area.   Easy assess to IH-35, I-10, for Forum shopping, healthcare, RAFB and Ft. Sam.  Exemplary School District.  This home is priced to sale quickly so bring your buyers and take a look.
